name: Tezos Help Desk
description: Photograph of the neon sign above the Tezos help desk art Miami Art Basel 2021. The sign hung above a desk where official Tezos helpers answered questions from the general public about Tezos. The help desk was off to the side next to the exhibition which displayed various works from NFT artists on the block chain. This exhibition is historic as it was the first time ever NFTs were exhibited at the main Basel fair. To the Moon!
